---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import logo from '../assets/logo.svg';
import reverbicAvatar from '../assets/reverbic-avatar.svg';
---

<Layout title="Reverbic - TUI Radio & Spotify Player">
	<main>
		<nav class="navbar glass">
			<div class="nav-content">
				<div class="logo-container">
					<img src={logo.src} alt="Reverbic" class="nav-logo" />
				</div>
				<div class="nav-links">
					<a href="https://github.com/sewandev/Reverbic" target="_blank" class="nav-link">GitHub</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/sewandev/Reverbic/releases" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline">Descargar</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<section class="hero">
			<div class="glow-effect"></div>
			<img src={reverbicAvatar.src} alt="Reverbic" class="hero-logo" />
			<h1>La terminal nunca sonó <span class="text-gradient">tan bien</span></h1>
			<p class="subtitle">
				Un reproductor ultraligero de Radio global, Spotify y YouTube directamente desde tu consola. Construido en Rust para Windows, macOS y Linux.
			</p>
			<div class="cta-group">
				<a href="https://github.com/sewandev/Reverbic/releases/latest" class="btn btn-primary">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
					Descargar
				</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/sewandev/Reverbic" class="btn btn-secondary glass">
					Ver código fuente
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="features">
			<h2 class="section-title">Características Principales</h2>
			<div class="grid">
				<div class="card glass">
					<div class="icon-wrapper">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/><path d="M16.24 7.76a6 6 0 0 1 0 8.49m-8.48-.01a6 6 0 0 1 0-8.49m11.31-2.82a10 10 0 0 1 0 14.14m-14.14 0a10 10 0 0 1 0-14.14"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Radio Global</h3>
					<p>Busca y reproduce miles de estaciones de radio por nombre, género o país al instante.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="card glass">
					<div class="icon-wrapper">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Control Spotify</h3>
					<p>Busca, reproduce, pausa y transfiere de dispositivo mediante control remoto (Premium requerido para reproducir).</p>
				</div>
				<div class="card glass">
					<div class="icon-wrapper">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2.5 17a24.12 24.12 0 0 1 0-10 2 2 0 0 1 1.4-1.4 49.56 49.56 0 0 1 16.2 0A2 2 0 0 1 21.5 7a24.12 24.12 0 0 1 0 10 2 2 0 0 1-1.4 1.4 49.55 49.55 0 0 1-16.2 0A2 2 0 0 1 2.5 17Z"/><path d="m10 15 5-3-5-3z"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>YouTube</h3>
					<p>Busca y reproduce audio directamente desde YouTube sin salir de la terminal.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="card glass">
					<div class="icon-wrapper">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="6" width="20" height="12" rx="2"/><path d="M6 12h4"/><path d="M8 10v4"/><line x1="15" y1="13" x2="15.01" y2="13"/><line x1="18" y1="11" x2="18.01" y2="11"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Gaming Overlay</h3>
					<p>Widget flotante con detección automática de juegos para ver qué está sonando sin interrumpir tus partidas.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="card glass">
					<div class="icon-wrapper">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Ligero y Rápido</h3>
					<p>Desarrollado en Rust. Consume apenas ~25MB de RAM y &lt;1% de CPU en reposo. Sin instaladores.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<footer class="glass">
			<p>Hecho con ❤️ por <a href="https://github.com/sewandev">sewandev</a></p>
		</footer>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0 1rem;
	}

	.navbar {
		width: 100%;
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		z-index: 100;
		padding: 1rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
	}

	.nav-content {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.logo-container {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.nav-logo {
		height: 32px;
		width: auto;
		object-fit: contain;
	}

	.nav-links {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.nav-link {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 500;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.nav-link:hover {
		color: white;
	}

	.hero {
		position: relative;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 10rem 1rem 6rem;
		max-width: 800px;
	}

	.glow-effect {
		position: absolute;
		top: 40%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
		width: 500px;
		height: 500px;
		background: var(--primary);
		filter: blur(140px);
		opacity: 0.25;
		z-index: -1;
		border-radius: 50%;
	}

	.hero-logo {
		width: 400px;
		max-width: 90vw;
		height: auto;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(23, 61, 220, 0.2));
		animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	@keyframes float {
		0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
		50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
		100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.1;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		letter-spacing: -1px;
	}

	.text-gradient {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #60a5fa, var(--primary));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		max-width: 600px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.cta-group {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: var(--primary);
		color: white;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(23, 61, 220, 0.4);
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		background: var(--primary-hover);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(23, 61, 220, 0.6);
	}

	.btn-secondary {
		color: white;
	}

	.btn-secondary:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.btn-outline {
		border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
		color: white;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
	}
	
	.btn-outline:hover {
		background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
	}

	.features {
		max-width: 1200px;
		width: 100%;
		padding: 4rem 1rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.card {
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 16px;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
	}

	.card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		border-color: rgba(23, 61, 220, 0.3);
	}

	.icon-wrapper {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		display: inline-flex;
		padding: 12px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		background: rgba(23, 61, 220, 0.1);
	}

	.card h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.card p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	
	footer {
		width: 100%;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2rem;
		margin-top: 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}
	
	footer a {
		color: var(--primary);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
		.nav-links {
			display: none;
		}
	}
</style>
